{
  "stem": "14552.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was just a very pleasant song.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think this would be awkward.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, but I--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--I sing it often.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and I-- and I just-- it just brings back the memories of that--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Shabbos afternoon.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was the [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] and the [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and then he would read-- sing Hebrew songs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when he was singing them, they were just-- they were just pleasant.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The time went very pleasantly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, then the [NON-ENGLISH] lighting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was the youngest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Therefore, I held my hand up high.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was holding the [NON-ENGLISH] and the, the little container for the nutmeg, the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was held high.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And everybody smelled it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, and the, the prayers over that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And after that was a bite to eat and to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because they opened the store for one more day-- one more hour.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Saturday, one more hour was open for good luck or little extra, cash or whatever because Sunday, stores were not open.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The store was in the middle of town, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a fairly modern-- it was the most modern structure they had.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a, a-- like a, a corridor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it had stores in it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It may have had 50 stores or more on each side of-- each side, they may have had 20, 25, 26 stores on each side.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from-- everything that you wanted, you could get there, linens and fabrics and hats and bags, and you name it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then there was this-- on the other end, there was this very famous shoe store, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was a big corner, a big store.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was-- it was a nice structure.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
